{"tid":1767203,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世][黃色經濟圈]大家可唔可以唔好再趕走變黃嘅藝人（如達哥）","createTime":"2019-12-03T06:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T09:34:00.000Z","uid":19334,"like":50,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8d952443d5db49fcea1c2eabb67ad46da6785d","tid":1767203,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"老實講，宜家肯發聲既KOL嘅比例真係唔高，Youtuber甚至得2-3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當有KOL開始表態轉黃嘅時候，總係有人質疑「宜家先表態，之前幾個月去咗邊啊？」等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現階段如果我地想壯大黃色經濟圈嘅話，比起質疑佢地付出得唔夠多之前，唔係更應該鼓勵佢地支持我地咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣keep住質疑只會趕走想轉黃嘅KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多一個朋友點都好過多一個敵人啊。<br />\n<br />\n天琦都講過「政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己」<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以少啲質疑，多啲支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(當然食人血饅頭嘅就唔計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望香港人，畀面大J，原諒林慧韡(達哥)，可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9e757a6bd324d6fe3c085c321568205b907fbc","tid":1767203,"uid":32454,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"一早原諒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ac5aa473a5ca528b3ebdbc3ebd73d194b9066e","tid":1767203,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f9e757a6bd324d6fe3c085c321568205b907fbc","tid":1767203,"uid":32454,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"一早原諒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3989d09293b3b10ebc89ffc9dd5035d57ec0b56e","tid":1767203,